根据以下参数显示达到 100% 磁盘容量所需的大约时间：\n\n* free d:
Shows the approximate time needed to reach 100% of disk capacity based on the following parameters:

* free disk space;
* row ingestion rate;
* dedup rate;
* compression.

Use this panel for capacity planning to estimate the remaining time until the disk space runs out.

